00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
You've been so nice to us.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
A lot of good people out there, so nice.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
We love you all so much.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
Thank you, you're such a blessing.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
Thank you for helping pray for us.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
We appreciate your prayers.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.650
I truly—I don't ever get into things, but I say thank you for the people who pray for me.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
I appreciate it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Pray for Diana, yes, it means a lot to us, so much.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
Prayers, it's a lot bigger than what you all realize for us, covering us and helping us.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
This whole thing has been really wild, and I'm just like, "Oh my goodness, thank you, Lord.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.650
" He's calling me up higher to do this, and I'm just like, "Okay, Lord, I'll do it for you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
" But we pray for all the things we've seen today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
God bless you all.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.350
Remember, put a smile on your face and a song in your heart, because Jesus loves you and we love you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
God bless you all, and we'll see you again tomorrow.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
Good night, bye-bye.
